use implementation 'com.tomer:fadingtextview:2.5' at app.gradle


make new file at res--->values

    at Values, rigr click--> new-->values resource file
    type your name of file, mybe like wordloppings


at wordloppings.xml, make this code

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<resources>
    <string-array name="Contoh">
        <item>ini</item>
        <item>adalah</item>
        <item>modul</item>
        <item>pembelajaran</item>
        <item>keep</item>
        <item>semangat</item>
        <item>belajar</item>
    </string-array>

</resources>



